{"id": 2176, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得哪些关于“婚恋”的惯用语其实都不太对劲？", "description": "乍一看是祝福是俗语是口口相传，仔细一想是天罗地网。", "record_count": 3745, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180211102633Sl7bO5WwZcfIdnmQ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-02-14T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 265218, "content": "直到目前家人还是认为结婚最重要的事就是生孩子(｡•́︿•̀｡) ", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697719}, {"id": 266242, "content": "某男长辈老年再婚说找老伴之前：也没有人收拾房子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262482}, {"id": 265219, "content": "该添一个了", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113647}, {"id": 265221, "content": "不婚女性/大龄未嫁女性会被称呼“老姑婆”", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253254}, {"id": 265222, "content": "男人一定要娶妻，女人一定要嫁人", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253254}, {"id": 265228, "content": "女孩子就应该被哄着\n\n久而久之，这样的女孩子就变成了宠物而不是一个人了", "image": null, "praise_count": 150, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1261323}, {"id": 268813, "content": "年纪到了就该结婚了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211383}, {"id": 265230, "content": "一个学业事业再成功的女性 只要过了适婚年龄还未嫁 就说明她有问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1257426}, {"id": 265231, "content": "男婚女嫁", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1261609}, {"id": 265233, "content": "男生就应该主动 就应该付账 就应该讨好准岳父岳母", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651076}, {"id": 265234, "content": "只要是节男的就要送礼物，新年，春节，情人节，圣诞节......，520，七夕tmd也算节了，女的只要晒就好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645237}, {"id": 265490, "content": "到了合适的年龄就要赶紧结婚了，不然变剩女没人要多丢人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262816}, {"id": 265491, "content": "也别太挑了，两个人都是互相磨合，能过日子就行，没那么多要求。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262816}, {"id": 265749, "content": "女的跟男的结婚就成为了男方的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1266477}, {"id": 265238, "content": "很讨厌“剩女”“大龄剩女”这些词，晚婚或者不婚的女性总是受到各种性别歧视", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1114562}, {"id": 265239, "content": "不用要求太高 搭伙过日子得磨合", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262448}, {"id": 265240, "content": "为什么男人不能嫁，女人不能娶？", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1222257}, {"id": 265241, "content": "“嫁给”这个词不奇怪吗？为什么男女结婚是女方被给予到男方？", "image": null, "praise_count": 73, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251294}, {"id": 265242, "content": "嫁鸡随鸡 嫁狗随狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262041}, {"id": 265243, "content": "男大当婚 女大当嫁\n不孝有三 无后为大", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 884724}, {"id": 265244, "content": "都多大了，还不结婚！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1261100}, {"id": 265250, "content": "太多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1116524}, {"id": 265251, "content": "居然有关键词。。ok 原文是 【where do I even start..  反正婚姻就是一纸契约嘛，任何名义的道德绑架都是违背人姓自you的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1116524}, {"id": 265252, "content": "娶嫁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1259985}, {"id": 265256, "content": "h", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262540}, {"id": 265257, "content": "婚礼上口口声声说愿意，没多久才发现不适合说离婚，你当结婚是什么？玩具？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262540}, {"id": 265513, "content": "“为了孩子也千万别离婚”\n我可去你的吧 你孩子盼着你们离呢知道吗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1264834}, {"id": 265258, "content": "懂得珍惜", "image": "img/option/option/20180215180608Xm1hov0VSMWA293Y", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1247714}, {"id": 265263, "content": "= = 我找不找对象关你屁事 - - 你是把结婚生子当生命目标的蠢货，我可不是，我要的是钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972975}, {"id": 265264, "content": "你这辈子总是要出门子嫁到人家的啊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1260711}, {"id": 265266, "content": "喜欢的人说啥都行，不想听的管你屁事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262557}, {"id": 265267, "content": "「男大当婚，女大当嫁。」？？？我年龄大为什么就必须结婚？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 586419}, {"id": 265269, "content": "我就不太明白，单身的为啥叫…狗………", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1256841}, {"id": 273206, "content": "“郎才女貌”Excuse me？？？WHY", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282875}, {"id": 265271, "content": "女同性恋咋啦？为什么不能给予一些理解和尊重？", "image": "img/option/option/201802152127086sRavtWZEK0qhiwj", "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195904}, {"id": 265272, "content": "都结婚了就别打扮了。哇？凭什么？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262589}, {"id": 265274, "content": "早生贵子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262595}, {"id": 265281, "content": "我是单身狗，所以我主张分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1115531}, {"id": 265284, "content": "父母想让你结婚的原因是怕丢人，女孩子的安全感完全琢磨不透", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 965413}, {"id": 265285, "content": "结婚是来过日子的，结婚前的感情可以不需要", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 965413}, {"id": 265286, "content": "父亲把女儿的手交到小伙手里眼中含泪“她的后半生交给你啦”【黑人问号脸】", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714076}, {"id": 265287, "content": "宁拆十座庙，不毁一粧婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 583590}, {"id": 265543, "content": "女权主义盛行压抑了整个婚恋观，为何不能平等？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1264987}, {"id": 265288, "content": "你爱嫁不嫁 没有逼你", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1254444}, {"id": 265290, "content": "差不多得了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 431874}, {"id": 265291, "content": "恋爱时期，你是“绝世美人”，被人称为“宝贝”；婚后，你是“发妻”，若有宠爱，则为“掌心宝”，若无，则为“仆人”。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262692}, {"id": 265292, "content": "为什么一定要结婚才有生孩子的权利？", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1135208}, {"id": 265293, "content": "难道不是找个异性结婚么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031917}, {"id": 265295, "content": "叫她吃卵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251547}, {"id": 265297, "content": "说破鞋的那位同学，突然想到王小波写的《黄金时代》，破鞋就破鞋，调侃之后大家也挺尊重破鞋的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234160}]}